# <BODY PART> Role

## Mission
What this body part owns and its primary objective.

## Inputs
What this body part reads, receives, or listens to.

## Outputs
What this body part produces, emits, or exports.

## Boundaries
What this body part must NOT do or handle.

## Canonical Paths
- Source: `BODY/<PART>/...`
- Sub-parts: `BODY/<PART>/<SUB-PART>/...`

## Bridge Surfaces
- List any wrappers or exports generated from this part.

## Verification
- How to prove this body part is correctly configured.

## Escalation
- Who to contact if this part encounters an error it cannot resolve.
